						p In 2022, due to continuing measures and investment projects to reduce water intake and water disposal, water consumption in the TATNEFT Group decreased by 5%. Due to the change in the approach to accounting for water losses, data for 2020, 2021 were recalculated for comparison.
						img(src="https://www.tatneft.ru/uploads/publications/dmpages/prilozheniya/processed_new_pictures/from_en/image22.jpg", alt="")

						p The measures aimed at increasing the share of recycled water used for production needs, as well as the timely repair of water supply networks allowed reducing the intake from surface sources by 2% or 1.2 million m3 year on year.


